snippet.title: SEGA AGES Space Harrier & Puyo Puyo | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The latest SEGA AGES titles are officially here! Blast off into the Fantasy Zone in Space Harrier or face off in some puzzling action in Puyo Puyo, available now exclusively on the Nintendo Switch.

Official website: https://segaages.sega.com/
